Using @SPodjasek's solution, I got an error about matching `arm-eabi` versus `arm64-sysv`. I think the best solution, that worked for me, is just building for 32 bit for the time being until this is all sorted out (@swavkulinski's solution [here](https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/18494#issuecomment-399155013)):

In your `app` level `build.gradle`:
```gradle
android {
    // ...
    buildTypes {
        release {
            // ...
            ndk {
                abiFilters "armeabi-v7a"
            }
        }
    }
}
```
